{"tid":820362,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"杜完牙根後 面腫","createTime":"2018-09-15T11:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T14:09:50.000Z","uid":61431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6841fbc70b20dca93d7c6863f9eedfba8338e4c4","tid":820362,"uid":61431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:20:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的， 我右邊上面第一臼齒(第4隻) 大約2年前做過杜牙根<br />\n<br />\n前排去洗牙檢查(第2個牙醫)，話個隻牙上面牙肉有牙瘡，係因為之前杜牙根做得唔夠徹底，仲有細菌造成。<br />\n<br />\n咁今日就去佐再做杜牙根啦，打佐麻醉，一度做都冇問題，唔覺得痛既<br />\n但做到尾段，個牙醫注射佐D野入去，就FEEL到痛楚由咀唇個位 痛到上右邊臉，之後我話痛，牙醫就停止注射，就同護士講清番出黎，咁痛楚就慢慢減少喇。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網睇番應該係消毒液 [次氯酸 Sodium Hypochlorite]<br />\n<br />\n整完之後牙醫就同我講，d殺菌液入佐個部份既組織，所以就feel到痛。<br />\n話應該1星期左右會消腫，期間要食消炎藥+止痛<br />\n<br />\n但返到屋企，個位仲feel到痛，訓完教起身，見到右邊臉好似仲腫佐 ，好似粒小魚蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問有冇巴絲打，識得/杜過牙根都試過咁，好擔心幾時先會消腫。上網搵，蘋果有報過 [氯酸鈉意外地破壞了牙齒組織，並導致嚴重發炎及腫脹] <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好驚，有冇人解答到我 係咪正常，會無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020e54561dae445d7c8299c39a3082cf09121b60","tid":820362,"uid":43361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:27:22.000Z","msg":"應該係Hypochlorite accident <br />\n要食抗生素,冷敷<br />\n多數10日左右冇事<br />\n如果轉差/嚴重要入醫院"},{"pid":"078010b20e0271f31bd04d694fa1cb3ce7ea9f63","tid":820362,"uid":61431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"020e54561dae445d7c8299c39a3082cf09121b60","tid":820362,"uid":43361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:27:22.000Z","msg":"應該係Hypochlorite accident <br />\n要食抗生素,冷敷<br />\n多數10日左右冇事<br />\n如果轉差/嚴重要入醫院"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:33:37.000Z","msg":"依種情況常唔常見的? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n牙醫叫我今日冷敷，聽日開始就熱敷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0f86289342e6abbb6718c775639c32aa60f0b9","tid":820362,"uid":208241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"其實即係漂白水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da3eb86ef21bdb096a929a9ebd801742815a8bb","tid":820362,"uid":61431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b0f86289342e6abbb6718c775639c32aa60f0b9","tid":820362,"uid":208241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"其實即係漂白水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:41:05.000Z","msg":"乜原來係漂白水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n面腫算唔算大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b496acf5c0e4ae790786d6557b3984a8071ec005","tid":820362,"uid":208241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2da3eb86ef21bdb096a929a9ebd801742815a8bb","tid":820362,"uid":61431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b0f86289342e6abbb6718c775639c32aa60f0b9","tid":820362,"uid":208241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"其實即係漂白水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:41:05.000Z","msg":"乜原來係漂白水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n面腫算唔算大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20